{"service_name": "Connection (CoCo) Assurance Services", "service_id": "6525682049875968", "company_name": "Selex ES Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Selex ES Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Connection (CoCo) Assurance Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    IA support services for organisations seeking technical connection to sensitive community networks and infrastructures, such as organisations seeking connection to PSN and PSN-P. CLAS staff will provide IA support attuned to the specific connection. Coco compliance, governance and management of technical risk are pre-requisites for gaining permission to connect.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Connection to PSN (Public Services Network) and PSN-P (PSN-Police)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent IA support attuned to a specific connection\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Satisfy CoCo compliance, governance and management of technical risk\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Create or update compliance statement (new or annual assessment)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Full coverage - physical, procedural, people and technical compliance assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Full decision support advice on possible resolution actions and timelines\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Addresses resolution for non-compliance found in mandated controls\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assist an organisation preparing for or during an audit\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Agreed representations to accreditors addressing the approach and risk control\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Creation and review of compliance statements to Codes of Connection\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Adept at highlighting gaps\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Facilitate technical connection to sensitive community networks and infrastructures\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Providing advice on the best VfM approach to meeting requirement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Assessments providing clients with feedback on viability of connection approach\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     An enduring service to support maintenance of connection through change\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3583 to \u00a31326 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/6525682049875968-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/6525682049875968-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/6525682049875968-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/6525682049875968-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6525\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6820\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      4987\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      5968\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       Selex ES Ltd\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Alex X Jardine\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"telephone\">\n       +44 (0) 117 900 8975\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemprop=\"email\">\n       <a data-event-category=\"Email a supplier\" data-event-label=\"Selex ES Ltd\" href=\"mailto:bid.co-ordination.SES@finmecc